<head2>(DECterm Options\customize_entry)


<P>
Once you have created a DECterm window, you  can choose operating features  
and then save these features by using the 
Options menu.  




                         
<head2>(Choosing Window Options\window)

<P>
Choose Window... from the Options menu to
change DECterm window features.  DECterm displays a 
dialog box.

<p>
In DECterm dialog boxes, shaded check buttons indicate the current settings.
<p>
