<le>Click on the Apply button to view your changes
without closing the dialog box.
<le>Click on the OK button to apply your changes
and close the dialog box.
<le>Click on the Cancel button to cancel your changes.
<le>Click on the Help button to get help on the displayed window.
<endlist>
