<head2>(Save Named Options...\save_as)

<P>


Choose Save Named Options... 
to save the current options with a new or different
file name.  DECterm displays a dialog box.

<p>
The dialog box prompts you for the name of the file you want to use to
save your options. The file list box displays the names of any
files in the current directory that contain selected options.
<condition>(vms)
By default, these files have the type DAT.
<endcondition>

<p>

