you want to copy by pressing and holding MB1, dragging the
pointer over the information, and releasing MB1.  Or, choose the 
Select All menu item from the Edit menu to copy the entire display.
<p>
The selected area is highlighted.

<le>Choose the Copy menu item from the Edit menu to store the copied 
information.

<le>Click on the area where you want to place the information.

<le>Choose the Paste menu item from the Edit menu.  
<endlist>
<p>
The selected information is copied to the new location.



