<ENDLIST>
 
<head3>(Print Text Page\print_page)
<p>
The Print Text Page option prints DECterm lines 1 through 24 as text.

<head3>(Print Selected Text\print_selected)
<p>
The Print Selected Text option 
prints the selected information.


<head3>(Print All Text\print_all)
<p>

The Print All Text option prints the information in  
the display and transcript as text.

<head3>(Print Graphics\print_graphics)
<p>
The Print Graphics option prints the contents of the display 
in Sixel format.


<head3>(Finish Printing\finish_printing)

<p>
The Finish Printing option completes a print job  
depending on the print destination.
If queued to a printer, the job is submitted.
If submitted to a dedicated printer port, 
the job is canceled. If written to a file,
the file is closed. This option is used with Auto 
Print mode or Printer Controller mode.  

<head3>(Cancel Printing\cancel_printing)
<p>

The Cancel Printing option stops the print request.


